            "id": "EXPORT_PROMOTION_CAPITAL_GOODS_EPCG_SCHEME_BENEFIT_01",
            "name": "Concessional/zero customs duty on capital goods against export obligation",
            "category": "tax_incentive",
            "summary": "Allows exporters to import capital goods (machinery, spares, moulds, software) at zero or concessional customs duty, in exchange for a commitment to export goods worth a multiple of the duty saved.",
            "calculation_logic": "Duty saved on imported capital goods, conditional on fulfilling an export obligation equal to 6 times the duty saved within 6 years (export obligation reduced by 25pct for indigenously sourced capital goods). IGST exemption also available on EPCG imports.",
